Jenkins Assignment - 02
Topics: User Authentication & User Authorization
📌 Overview

This project demonstrates Jenkins security configuration, including:

User Authentication (creating multiple users)
User Authorization (role-based access control)
Job segregation based on teams
Implementation of different Jenkins authorization strategies
Google SSO integration for admin user
🏢 Organization Structure

The organization is divided into 3 teams:

👨‍💻 Developer Team
⚙️ DevOps Team
🧪 Testing Team

Each team has restricted or controlled access based on roles.

