🔐 Authorization Strategy Implementation
🧠 Strategies Explored
1. Legacy Mode
Old Jenkins security model
Not role-based
❌ Not recommended
2. Project-Based Matrix Authorization
Permissions defined per project
Useful for small setups
Limited scalability
3. Matrix-Based Security
Global + project-level permissions
Fine-grained control
Complex to manage
4. Role-Based Authorization (Recommended)
Uses roles like:
Developer
DevOps
Testing
Admin
Clean and scalable
Easy to maintain
✅ Implemented Strategy

👉 Role-Based Authorization Strategy (Recommended Plugin: Role Strategy Plugin)

📸 Screenshot Section (Authorization)
### 📷 Authorization Strategy Configuration
