🔑 Permissions Summary
👨‍💻 Developer Role
View dev jobs only
Build jobs
View workspace
Configure jobs
🧪 Testing Role
View test jobs
View dev jobs
Build jobs
Configure jobs
Workspace access
⚙️ DevOps Role
View dev + test + devops jobs
Full build access
Configure jobs
Workspace access
🛡️ Admin Role
Full access to Jenkins
Manage users
Manage jobs
Configure system
🔐 Part 2: Google SSO Integration
🌐 Objective

Enable Google Single Sign-On (SSO) for the admin user.

⚙️ Steps Implemented
Installed Google OAuth Plugin
Configured Google Cloud Console credentials
Set:
Client ID
Client Secret
Allowed domain authentication
Assigned admin access to Google user
